<lb ed="L" n="0590a01"/><cb:juan fun="close" n="6"><cb:jhead>龍池幻有禪師語錄卷之六</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="L" n="0590a02"/><cb:div type="w"><head>音釋</head>
<lb ed="L" n="0590a03"/><cb:div type="note"><entry><form>頰</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0590a0302" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">吉<term rend="no_nor">恊</term>切音筴面旁也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>舶</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0590a0311" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">簿陌切音白海中大船</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>挖</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0590a0321" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">馬刮切音斡挑挖也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry>
<lb ed="L" n="0590a04"/><entry><form>懵懂</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0590a0403" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">上母總切音蠓下多動切音董心亂也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>髑髏</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0590a0420" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">上杜谷切音獨下<anchor xml:id="beg_4d" type="cb-app"/>落<anchor xml:id="end_4d"/>
<lb ed="L" n="0590a05"/>侯切音樓髑髏頂也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>疣</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL153p0590a0510" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">于求切音由贅也結肉也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
